# Carrick — Webflow + Commerce7 (C7)

Webflow site with Commerce7 integration. **Not Next.js.** There is no app build step — only CSS and JS assets.

## Constraints

- No access to the C7 backend or admin. All UI changes are done with CSS/JS against C7-rendered DOM.
- C7 owns routes under `/profile` (e.g. `/profile`, `/profile/login`, `/profile/account`), `/shop`, and `/cart`.
- Staging URLs:
  - Profile: https://carrick-6a9492.webflow.io/profile
  - Shop: https://carrick-6a9492.webflow.io/shop
  - Cart: https://carrick-6a9492.webflow.io/cart
- C7 loads via: `https://cdn.commerce7.com/beta/commerce7.js` (`data-tenant="carrick-winery"`).
- C7 swaps views client-side — site-wide scripts must use `MutationObserver` and survive DOM re-renders.
- Scope styles with `body:has(.c7-…)` selectors so rules apply after C7 injects markup.
- Font `@import` for Albert Sans lives in the Webflow site head — do not duplicate in CSS files.

## Hosting & deployment

Assets live in this repo and are served to Webflow via **jsDelivr** (GitHub CDN). The user pushes to GitHub; Webflow loads the files by URL. **Do not tell the user to copy-paste file contents into Webflow** — only edit the source files here.

- **Repo:** https://github.com/cubdigital/carrick-c7.git
- **Branch:** `main`

### Webflow Site Settings → Custom Code
**Head:**
```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cubdigital/carrick-c7@main/sitewide.css">
```

**Footer:**
```html
<script defer type="text/javascript" src="https://cdn.commerce7.com/beta/commerce7.js" id="c7-javascript" data-tenant="carrick-winery"></script>
<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cubdigital/carrick-c7@main/sitewide.js"></script>
```

Route-specific assets use the same CDN pattern when linked from page settings.

### `/profile` page → Custom Code
**Head:** `profile-head.css` via jsDelivr

### `/shop` page → Custom Code
**Head:**
```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cubdigital/carrick-c7@main/shop-head.css">
```

**Footer:**
```html
<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cubdigital/carrick-c7@main/shop-script.js"></script>
```

### `/cart` page → Custom Code
**Head:**
```html
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cubdigital/carrick-c7@main/cart-head.css">
```

**Footer:**
```html
<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/cubdigital/carrick-c7@main/cart-script.js"></script>
```

## Source files (edit these)

| File | Scope | Loaded from |
|------|-------|-------------|
| `sitewide.css` | Site-wide C7 overrides (login, profile, shop add-to-cart, shared layout) | Site Settings → Head |
| `sitewide.js` | Site-wide behaviour (age gate, profile/login DOM wrappers, cart, observers) | Site Settings → Footer |
| `profile-head.css` | `/profile` dashboard-only styles | `/profile` page → Custom Code → Head |
| `profile-before-body.html` | Legacy inline script — prefer moving logic into `sitewide.js` or a `.js` file |
| `shop-head.css` | `/shop` page styles (filter buttons, View All, product cards) | `/shop` page → Custom Code → Head |
| `shop-script.js` | `/shop` behaviour (View All toggle, C7 tile filter, product card hydration) | `/shop` page → Custom Code → Footer |
| `cart-head.css` | `/cart` page styles (3-column layout, empty/populated cart states) | `/cart` page → Custom Code → Head |
| `cart-script.js` | `/cart` behaviour (empty-cart message formatting, DOM observer) | `/cart` page → Custom Code → Footer |

**Use `.css` and `.js` files only.** Do not create HTML wrapper files with `<script>` or `<style>` tags unless the user explicitly asks.

## Agent workflow

1. Edit the relevant `.css` or `.js` file directly.
2. Keep changes scoped and minimal — match existing patterns in the file.
3. Remind the user to `git push` to `main` when done; Webflow picks up changes after jsDelivr cache refreshes (~minutes).
4. For an immediate CDN update, pin jsDelivr to a commit hash instead of `@main`.

## C7 DOM reference

### Profile

- Login: `.c7-account-login`
- Dashboard: `.c7-account__dashboard`, `.c7-account-tile__section`
- Custom wrappers added by our JS: `.carrick-dashboard-intro`, `.carrick-tile-row`, `.carrick-profile-layout`

### Shop

Webflow CMS markup + C7 product hydration via `shop-script.js`. Key data attributes:

- Section / View All: `[data-shop-section]`, `[data-shop-view-all]`, `[data-shop-item]`, `[data-shop-expanded]`
- Collection filter: `[data-shop-filter]`, `[data-shop-filter-results]`, `[data-shop-results-section]`, `[data-shop-results-heading]`, `[data-shop-empty]`
- Product cards: `[data-c7-card]`, `[data-c7-product-slug]`, `[data-c7-collection-id]`, `[data-c7-image]`, `[data-c7-price]`, `[data-c7-link]`, `[data-c7-title]`, `[data-c7-product-subtitle]`
- Add to cart (sitewide): `.shop-product-add-to-cart .c7-product__variant__add-to-cart`, `.c7-button`

### Cart

C7 cart page mounted in `#c7-content`. Key selectors:

- Wrapper / layout: `#c7-content`, `.c7-cart__wrapper`, `.c7-cart__buttons--top`
- Empty state: `.c7-message--empty-cart`, `.c7-empty-cart-text`, `.c7-empty-cart-button`
- Populated cart: `.c7-cart__items`, `.c7-cart__items-container`, `.c7-cart__form`, `.c7-cart__summary`, `.c7-cart__totals`, `.c7-cart__footer`, `.c7-cart__buttons`, `.c7-cart__item`, `.c7-cart__row`
- Custom JS: `carrickFormatEmptyCartMessage()` — uses `MutationObserver` to survive C7 re-renders
